<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV47">
<l>kāroṭotta mēṉinaṅkaḷ kaṇṇa. viṇṇi ṉātaṉē</l>
<l>nīriṭatta rāvaṇaikki ṭattiyeṉpa raṉṟiyum</l>
<l>ōriṭattai yallaiyellai yillaiyeṉpa rātalāl</l>
<l>cērviṭattai nāyiṉēṉ ṟerintiṟaiñcu mācolē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Kṛṣṇa with a cloud-like body! O Lord of the sky!</l>
<l>They say that You lie upon a serpent bed upon the water. Besides,</l>
<l>They say that You do not belong to one place, that there are no limits</l>
<l rend="indent">[as to where You live]. Therefore,</l>
<l>Tell [me] how I, a dog, [can] learn about the place to reach and pay reverence!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
